<body>
  <%- include("component/navbar.ejs") %>

  <header class="insight-header">
    <h1>📈 Market Insights</h1>
    <p>Tips and knowledge to help you understand agricultural market trends and maximize your profits.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="tips-container">

    <div class="tip-card">
      <h2>🌾 Understand Seasonal Demand</h2>
      <p>Track when certain crops are in high demand. Off-season pricing can yield 2x profits. Plan sowing and harvesting accordingly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-card">
      <h2>📉 Watch Mandis & Market Price Trends</h2>
      <p>Check daily prices across mandis to identify trends. Sell when the trend is upward, and avoid panic selling on sudden dips.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-card">
      <h2>📦 Store Smartly for Price Peaks</h2>
      <p>If you can store your crops safely for 2–3 weeks, wait for price peaks post-harvest rush. Especially useful for onions, pulses, and potatoes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-card">
      <h2>🧑‍🌾 Diversify Crops</h2>
      <p>Don’t rely on just one crop. A mix of high-margin and fast-sale crops ensures stability even if one market crashes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tip-card">
      <h2>📊 Use FarmSarthi Trends</h2>
      <p>We analyze regional data to recommend best-selling crops. Stay updated in the dashboard or upcoming insights tool.</p>
    </div>

  </section>
  <%- include('component/footer.ejs') %>
